templates.template: MATCH (a:$LABEL1 {$PROP1: $VALUE}), (b:$LABEL2) WHERE NOT (a)-[:$REL]->(b) WITH b ORDER BY b.$PROP_ID LIMIT 32 RETURN b.$PROP_ID
templates.anti_template: MATCH (a:$LABEL1 {$PROP1: $VALUE}), (b:$LABEL2) WHERE (a)-[:$REL]->(b) WITH b ORDER BY b.$PROP_ID LIMIT 32 RETURN b.$PROP_ID

templates.template: MATCH (a:$LABEL1) WHERE (a)-[:$REL_TYPE]->(:$LABEL2) WITH a RETURN collect(a.$RETURN_PROP)[0..1] AS values
templates.anti_template: MATCH (a:$LABEL1) WHERE NOT (a)-[:$REL_TYPE]->(:$LABEL2) WITH a RETURN collect(a.$RETURN_PROP)[0..1] AS values

templates.template: MATCH (a:$LABEL) WHERE NOT a.$PROP $OP $VALUE WITH a ORDER BY a.$PROP_ID LIMIT 10 RETURN a.$PROP_ID
templates.anti_template: MATCH (a:$LABEL) WHERE a.$PROP $OP $VALUE WITH a ORDER BY a.$PROP_ID LIMIT 10 RETURN a.$PROP_ID

templates.template: MATCH (a:$LABEL) WHERE NOT a.$PROP $OP $VALUE WITH a RETURN collect(a.$RET_PROP)[0..1] AS vals
templates.anti_template: MATCH (a:$LABEL) WHERE a.$PROP $OP $VALUE WITH a RETURN collect(a.$RET_PROP)[0..1] AS vals

templates.template: MATCH (a:$LABEL) WHERE NOT (a)-[:$REL1]->(:$LABEL2) OR (a)-[:$REL2]->(:$LABEL3) WITH a RETURN collect(a.$RET_PROP)[0..1] AS vals
MATCH (a:$LABEL1)-[:$REL]-()-[:$REL]-(b:$LABEL2) WHERE NOT (a)-[:$REL]-(b) WITH b ORDER BY b.$PROP_ID LIMIT 10 RETURN b.$PROP_ID
templates.anti_template: MATCH (a:$LABEL1)-[:$REL]-()-[:$REL]-(b:$LABEL2) WHERE (a)-[:$REL]-(b) WITH b ORDER BY b.$PROP_ID LIMIT 10 RETURN b.$PROP_ID
